<h1>L'Aurore</h1>
<p>“L’Aurore” is a French name for “The Dawn”.</p>
<p>It’s a music production and post sound production studio.</p>
<p>“Take your project from dawn to noon”</p>



<%= image_tag ("l_aurore_home_photo.jpg") %>

<p>Its founder Geoffrey Papin has studied acoustic physics and sound technology followed by a degree at the famous French jazz school “Jazz à Tours”. He is a multi-instrumentalist, composer and producer who worked for Thylacine, Tiger Lion, La Houle..etc. And a sound designer, post sound mixer for advertisings, films, or documentaries. He is also founder of the band “Sisyphes” as a guitarist-singer.</p>

<p>Geoffrey Papin is a very adaptive person with a sharp eye for details, using his skills as an artist,  musician, and technician to bring together a fine and global point of view on your sound-requirements. Always curious and keen to discover some new sound fields in a friendly atmosphere, he is a mindful partner in any of your projects.</p>